                                                  SIMULATION OF
                         SES v4.1 file for testing the reading and conversion of forms.
                         Handles most forms - only ones missing are 6H (weird, causes a crash),
                         4A (this is an aero/thermo run not a fire run), 8C (gradients),
                         8D (train stopping points), 9F to 9L (train performance) and
                         10 (stationary trains).
                         A case with tpopt=3; explicit speed-time, explicit heat gain calculation
                         Humidity displayed as kg/kg of dry air
                         Print option set to zero (designer oriented output)
